#import potential yields
potentialYields <- raster("data/Energieleistungsdichte-100m_EPSG25832_TIFF/en_100m_klas.tif")
summary(potentialYields)

plot(potentialYields, sub = "Fig. ", main = "Potential yields of NRW")

#create subset of wind turbines for each precinct
windTurbinesArnsberg <- st_intersection(windTurbines, precincts[precincts$GN == "Arnsberg",])
windTurbinesDetmold <- st_intersection(windTurbines, precincts[precincts$GN == "Detmold",])
windTurbinesKln <- st_intersection(windTurbines, precincts[precincts$GN == "Kln",])
windTurbinesDsseldorf <- st_intersection(windTurbines, precincts[precincts$GN == "Dsseldorf",])
windTurbinesMnster <- st_intersection(windTurbines, precincts[precincts$GN == "Mnster",])

#create planar point patterns from wind turbine subsets
pppArnsberg <- as.ppp(c(st_geometry(precincts[precincts$GN == "Arnsberg",]), st_geometry(windTurbinesArnsberg)))
pppDetmold <- as.ppp(c(st_geometry(precincts[precincts$GN == "Detmold",]), st_geometry(windTurbinesDetmold)))
pppKln <- as.ppp(c(st_geometry(precincts[precincts$GN == "Kln",]), st_geometry(windTurbinesKln)))
pppDsseldorf <- as.ppp(c(st_geometry(precincts[precincts$GN == "Dsseldorf",]), st_geometry(windTurbinesDsseldorf)))
pppMnster <- as.ppp(c(st_geometry(precincts[precincts$GN == "Mnster",]), st_geometry(windTurbinesMnster)))

precintNames <- c("Arnsberg", "Detmold", "Kln", "Dsseldorf", "Mnster")
windTurbineCounts <- c(pppArnsberg$n, pppDetmold$n, pppKln$n, pppDsseldorf$n, pppMnster$n)
windTurbineDensities <- c(pppArnsberg$n/(as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Arnsberg",]))/1000000), 
                          pppDetmold$n/(as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Detmold",]))/1000000), 
                          pppKln$n/(as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Kln",]))/1000000),
                          pppDsseldorf$n/(as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Dsseldorf",]))/1000000),
                          pppMnster$n/(as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Mnster",]))/1000000))
precintAreas <- c(as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Arnsberg",]))/1000000,
                  as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Detmold",]))/1000000,
                  as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Kln",]))/1000000,
                  as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Dsseldorf",]))/1000000,
                  as.numeric(st_area(precincts[precincts$GN == "Mnster",]))/1000000)

precinctDf <- data.frame(precintNames, precintAreas, windTurbineCounts, windTurbineDensities)
colnames(precinctDf) <- c('Precinct','Area in km','Turbine count', 'Turbine density')

#compute densities of wind turbines for each precinct
densityArnsberg <- density(pppArnsberg, sigma = bw.diggle, diggle = TRUE, edge = TRUE)
densityDetmold <- density(pppDetmold, sigma = bw.diggle, diggle = TRUE, edge = TRUE)
densityKln <- density(pppKln, sigma = bw.diggle, diggle = TRUE, edge = TRUE)
densityDsseldorf <- density(pppDsseldorf, sigma = bw.diggle, diggle = TRUE, edge = TRUE)
densityMnster <- density(pppMnster, sigma = bw.diggle, diggle = TRUE, edge = TRUE)

Part II - Influence of potenial energy yields

#import precincts
yields <- c("1", "2", "3", "4", "5", "6", "7")

#extract yields
turbinesWithYieldsArnsberg <- as.data.frame(extract(potentialYieldsArnsbergMasked, windTurbinesArnsberg))
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsArnsberg) <- c("DN")

turbinesWithYieldsDetmold <- as.data.frame(extract(potentialYieldsDetmoldMasked, windTurbinesDetmold))
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsDetmold) <- c("DN")

turbinesWithYieldsKln <- as.data.frame(extract(potentialYieldsKlnMasked, windTurbinesKln))
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsKln) <- c("DN")

turbinesWithYieldsDsseldorf <- as.data.frame(extract(potentialYieldsDsseldorfMasked, windTurbinesDsseldorf))
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsDsseldorf) <- c("DN")

turbinesWithYieldsMnster <- as.data.frame(extract(potentialYieldsMnsterMasked, windTurbinesMnster))
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsMnster) <- c("DN")

#compute turbine count per yield
turbinesWithYieldsArnsbergFreq <- count(turbinesWithYieldsArnsberg) 
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsArnsbergFreq) <- c("potentialYield", "turbineCount")

turbinesWithYieldsDetmoldFreq <- count(turbinesWithYieldsDetmold) 
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsDetmoldFreq) <- c("potentialYield", "turbineCount")

turbinesWithYieldsKlnFreq <- count(turbinesWithYieldsKln) 
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsKlnFreq) <- c("potentialYield", "turbineCount")

turbinesWithYieldsDsseldorfFreq <- count(turbinesWithYieldsDsseldorf) 
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsDsseldorfFreq) <- c("potentialYield", "turbineCount")

turbinesWithYieldsMnsterFreq <- count(turbinesWithYieldsMnster) 
colnames(turbinesWithYieldsMnsterFreq) <- c("potentialYield", "turbineCount")

#compute pixel counts per yield
potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts <-  as.data.frame(freq(potentialYieldsArnsbergMasked))
colnames(potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts) <- c("potentialYield", "pixelCount")

potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts <-  as.data.frame(freq(potentialYieldsDetmoldMasked))
colnames(potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts) <- c("potentialYield", "pixelCount")

potentialYieldsKlnCounts <-  as.data.frame(freq(potentialYieldsKlnMasked))
colnames(potentialYieldsKlnCounts) <- c("potentialYield", "pixelCount")

potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts <-  as.data.frame(freq(potentialYieldsDsseldorfMasked))
colnames(potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts) <- c("potentialYield", "pixelCount")

potentialYieldsMnsterCounts <-  as.data.frame(freq(potentialYieldsMnsterMasked))
colnames(potentialYieldsMnsterCounts) <- c("potentialYield", "pixelCount")

#compute area per yield
potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts$area = (potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts$pixelCount*10000)/1000000
potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts$area = (potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts$pixelCount*10000)/1000000
potentialYieldsKlnCounts$area = (potentialYieldsKlnCounts$pixelCount*10000)/1000000
potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts$area = (potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts$pixelCount*10000)/1000000
potentialYieldsMnsterCounts$area = (potentialYieldsMnsterCounts$pixelCount*10000)/1000000

#merge turbine counts per yield and pixel counts per yield
potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts <- merge(turbinesWithYieldsArnsbergFreq, potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts, 
                                       by.x = "potentialYield", by.y = "potentialYield")

potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts <- merge(turbinesWithYieldsDetmoldFreq, potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts, 
                                      by.x = "potentialYield", by.y = "potentialYield")

potentialYieldsKlnCounts <- merge(turbinesWithYieldsKlnFreq, potentialYieldsKlnCounts, 
                                      by.x = "potentialYield", by.y = "potentialYield")

potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts <- merge(turbinesWithYieldsDsseldorfFreq, potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts, 
                                      by.x = "potentialYield", by.y = "potentialYield")

potentialYieldsMnsterCounts <- merge(turbinesWithYieldsMnsterFreq, potentialYieldsMnsterCounts, 
                                      by.x = "potentialYield", by.y = "potentialYield")

potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts$density = potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts$turbineCount/potentialYieldsArnsbergCounts$area
potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts$density = potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts$turbineCount/potentialYieldsDetmoldCounts$area
potentialYieldsKlnCounts$density = potentialYieldsKlnCounts$turbineCount/potentialYieldsKlnCounts$area
potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts$density = potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts$turbineCount/potentialYieldsDsseldorfCounts$area
potentialYieldsMnsterCounts$density = potentialYieldsMnsterCounts$turbineCount/potentialYieldsMnsterCounts$area
